OpenNI
------

Website: http://structure.io/openni

Building Prerequisites
======================

Windows
-------
- Microsoft Visual Studio (2022)
- Microsoft Kinect SDK v1.8 (X360) & v2.0 (XBONE)
- vcpkg or NuGet to install boost.interprocess

Building
========
Building on Windows:
  Install boost-interprocess:x64-windows-static
  Open the solution OpenNI.sln and build all

Important
=========
Great thanks to [korejan](https://github.com/korejan) for modifying OpenNI/Kinect2  
to work properly and support NiTE, *yaaaaaaaaaaaaaay!*